Homepage:  http://www.florian-diesch.de/software/arronax/
X-Python-Version: >= 2.7


Package: arronax
Architecture: all
X-Python-Version: >= 2.7
Depends: arronax-base
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax lets you create and modify starters (*.desktop files) for
 aplications, files, and URIs.	     
 .
 This is a metapackage that depends on the standalone version of
 Arronax. It doesn't contain any important files and may be removed
 without doing any harm.


Package: arronax-base
Architecture: all
X-Python-Version: >= 2.7
Depends:  ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gir1.2-glib-2.0,  gir1.2-gtk-3.0, python-gobject (>= 2.90), gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0, python-pkg-resources, python-xdg
Conflicts: arronax (<= 0.03)
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax lets you create and modify starters (*.desktop files) for
 applications, files, and URIs.
 .
 This package contains the standalone version of Arronax. 


Package: arronax-nautilus
Architecture: all
X-Python-Version: >= 2.7
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python (>=2.7) , arronax-base, nautilus (>= 3.4.1), python-nautilus
Conflicts: arronax (<= 0.03)
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax lets you create and modify starters (*.desktop files) for
 applications, files, and URIs.
 .
 This package contains the Nautilus plugin for Arronax. It adds a 
 "Create starter" menu item to the Desktop's context menu and to the file 
 context menu in Nautilus


