Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax lets you create and modify starters (*.desktop files) for
 applications, files, and URIs.
 .
 This package contains the Caja plugin for Arronax. It adds a 
 "Create starter" menu item to the Desktop's context menu and to the file 
 context menu in Caja


